Installation
------------

– First you need PHP 5.2 and a MySQL Database to use Facturier
– Create a MySQL database
– Install MySQL tables (facturier.sql)
– Modify acces/cle.php according to your system

Configuration
-------------

— Load index.php in a browser
— Click on Préférences and enter your informations
— Click on Clients and add a first Client

Now you are ready to create invoices.